title: Riverwest Co-op Grocery
description: Community-based, member-owned, volunteer-run, not-for-profit natural foods grocery store and cafe that is open to the public. Carries all organic produce, a wide selection of vegetarian and vegan groceries, bulk foods, pet food, child care, health and beauty, locally produced soaps, crafts and candles. Cafe is serves vegetarian and vegan foods. Parking available.
